6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to railroads; defining terms;
requiring certain documents and identification to
8 operate a train; mandating penalties; requiring
certain types of notice for violations; allowing
9 certain department to assess penalties; directing all
monies collected to be deposited in certain fund;
10 providing for codification; and providing an
effective date.
